*pmount-0.9.11 (16 Jun 2006)

  16 Jun 2006; Steev Klimaszewski <steev@gentoo.org> +pmount-0.9.11.ebuild:
  Version bump to 0.9.11.  Closes Bug 136694.  Thanks to Daniel Webert
  <rockoo@gmail.com> for the report.

  29 Apr 2006; Steev Klimaszewski <steev@gentoo.org> pmount-0.9.9.ebuild:
  hal now does the keepdir on /media so that we don't get collisions from pmount
  and gnome-mount (which can co-exist). Bug 130795.

*pmount-0.9.9 (28 Apr 2006)

  28 Apr 2006; Steev Klimaszewski <steev@gentoo.org> +pmount-0.9.9.ebuild:
  New upstream release of pmount.  Fixes some bugs with hal 0.5.7

